data.value:
Although it is called iced tea, a delicious cocktail with the color and taste of black tea is prepared without using half a drop of black tea. It's quite high in alcohol, so don't be fooled by the sweetness of the curacao, lemon juice and cola.
Base wine: Tequila (30ml) Vodka (30ml) Ingredients: Lemon Juice (20ml)
Price: £5
